snippet.title: Wayfinder:  Dev Diary #01 - Early Access Begins Aug 15
snippet.description:
►► Wishlist Wayfinder on PlayStation Today: https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10002172 
►► Wishlist Wayfinder on Steam Today: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1171690/Wayfinder/

Gloom Break: Founder’s Season 1 begins August 15! Join Early Access with any Founder’s Pack purchase.

The Airship Syndicate team shares brand new Early Access information you’ve been waiting for!

Are you ready to #ControltheChaos and defend against the Gloom? Don’t forget to wishlist Wayfinder today, and become a Founder on August 15!

#Wayfinder #GloomBreak
